{"tid":689536,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚睇完HOTCHA人生無憾了","createTime":"2018-06-04T07:04:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T16:14:48.000Z","uid":164242,"like":20,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b101769091daedf4fcbb844f159e0ae42de9aa","tid":689536,"uid":164242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:04:52.000Z","msg":"長文慎入<br />\n<br />\n我明白冇留意佢地 冇睇住佢地成長既人<br />\n可能會覺得: 單飛撈唔起,冇睇頭冇星味,出黎扮fd 搵銀.....<br />\n<br />\n但作為一個真係足足十一年既fans黎講<br />\n今次concert真係超額完成 <br />\n好多歌舞都重現舞台<br />\n帶左好多回憶感覺返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n完全值回票價<br />\n<br />\n三個人都各有三十歲 仲咁短時間內排舞練歌<br />\n初頭擔心佢地冇咁既氣力 體力 默契 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想像到搞演唱會有幾大困難同壓力<br />\n但結果幾surprised 冇乜大走音甩beat跳錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唱跳黎講 香港我真係數唔出有邊個係得....<br />\n<br />\n歌方面我以為好多人都唔熟悉<br />\n點知琴晚最hit果幾首歌<br />\n好多人跟住大合唱同企起身<br />\n冇歌詞都好多人識唱 氣氛好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感覺到好熱血好青春返左十年前咁款<br />\n<br />\n可惜既係有啲幾好聽既歌冇唱<br />\n煙花祭 好姊妹 冰封 流淚是會感染的 白色手機 八八伴 一二三 門外門內........<br />\n但最正係有唯一的你！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zzog-SnV6qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fzzog-SnV6qg&d=gqSN%2BKN5GisA85iYsxYcAQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=fc34a70a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zzog-SnV6qg</a><br />\n<br />\n不足既都有<br />\n例如冇啦啦cut左C講野果part, Solo 部分好似太多, Chilam 做嘉賓唱得好hea.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為有I love you boys 合唱火熱悶棍lalala <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4wqZxn9YK68\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4wqZxn9YK68&d=gqSN%2BKN5GisA85iYsxYcAQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=d97b1329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4wqZxn9YK68</a><br />\n<br />\n以有有啤梨合唱時光之光<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rviez_4Yzu4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRviez_4Yzu4&d=gqSN%2BKN5GisA85iYsxYcAQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=43f4c85d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rviez_4Yzu4</a><br />\n<br />\n不過點都好啦<br />\n十年後見到呢個logo 重現大舞台<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/150026_55cde9e6594e589544501e77789aabe1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F150026_55cde9e6594e589544501e77789aabe1.png&h=e270ed7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n心情真係好滾動 <br />\n仲有三個初出道 十八廿二既相同跳舞片<br />\n都幾催淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然唔係咩大明星 半紅半紫又多不和新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但琴晚埸concert的確完左唔少hotcha死忠既追星舞<br />\n(之前以為佢地冇機會再重組)<br />\n仲勾返以前小學好多美好回憶同果份正能量<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/150108_a1806346ad1502742644c66ee4e9e1c2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F150108_a1806346ad1502742644c66ee4e9e1c2.png&h=06eb7ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後生真係無敵 見到走樣好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好耐冇試過睇完一場show之後覺得咁熱血<br />\n<br />\n利申: Hotcha 11年死忠 但當時太細 冇去佢地第一場九展show 亦冇join fans club 活動 <br />\n但默默支持左十年 <br />\n琴晚已嗌沙喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/150153_7f103ee46002f956d6994552f8f547f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F150153_7f103ee46002f956d6994552f8f547f7.png&h=affb8c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n借圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f25c2baa435aa64f6e93b60be8920e821fc953","tid":689536,"uid":164242,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:10:29.000Z","msg":"仲有佢地三個人把聲辨識度高，各自有自己style <br />\n唔似啲韓團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個人造人冇黎特色<br />\n唔係話hotcha 打手 只係琴晚睇完concert有感而發<br />\n覺得佢地潛力好大 如果當初冇散同公司捧下 <br />\n今日唔知會點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4104a3c13065eced97e65846068b55f58e6991c","tid":689536,"uid":130056,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"same here<br />\n睇完琴晚個show<br />\n我更加相信佢地當年就算真係有不和 依家都一定已經和好番<br />\n琴晚佢地真係好有默契 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試問有邊個可以好似佢地咁又跳又唱都無咩失準 <br />\nd歌前奏一起 回憶已經番曬黎 <br />\n嗌歌嗌到聲沙 無憾了 <br />\n好想佢地可以一直以HotCha名義行落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015d0db182ee16e1ac08d1c020b5eb94a5d649ec","tid":689536,"uid":164242,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4104a3c13065eced97e65846068b55f58e6991c","tid":689536,"uid":130056,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"same here<br />\n睇完琴晚個show<br />\n我更加相信佢地當年就算真係有不和 依家都一定已經和好番<br />\n琴晚佢地真係好有默契 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試問有邊個可以好似佢地咁又跳又唱都無咩失準 <br />\nd歌前奏一起 回憶已經番曬黎 <br />\n嗌歌嗌到聲沙 無憾了 <br />\n好想佢地可以一直以HotCha名義行落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"感動都喊左出黎，男朋友話我誇張，外人根本唔明粉絲有幾滾動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2885302a6f557885f1cbcfce0c497ff1f8c1ec84","tid":689536,"uid":139381,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:14:54.000Z","msg":"唔知點解感受到樓主個種遺憾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：hotcha出道咁耐冇乜留意過"},{"pid":"7d1403ae9ace3e5613179ddfc3c117a75cb8e050","tid":689536,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:17:28.000Z","m